features: The Ultimate Vitamin C Supplement: FlavCity’s C-Ya later! Vitamin C capsules are derived from real food sources. Not only can Vitamin C help support your immune system, but it can also help your body form blood vessels, build cartilage and muscle, and create collagen in your bones. One bottle includes 30 servings.

Best-in-Class Ingredients: Packed with bioavailable food sources such as acerola (which has 9x more Vitamin C than oranges), camu camu, and amla berry, our ultimate Vitamin C supplement offers 500% of the recommended daily value. Harnessing the power of natural flavonoids, C-Ya later! can help provide a powerful shield for your wellness throughout the year.
How to Take: Our Vitamin C supplement comes in an easy-to-swallow capsule. We recommend taking 2 capsules daily.

We Got You: Every FlavCity product is meticulously crafted with a passion for flavor and a commitment to quality. Each ingredient has been thoroughly researched and every product has passed stringent quality control measures to provide you with peace of mind. If it’s “Bobby Approved,” you know you’re in good hands.

About Us: Since 2012, Bobby Parrish has amassed a following of more than 12 million community members by creating online food and wellness content and authoring popular cookbooks. His mission is to help people know exactly what they put in their bodies so they can thrive.
body.description: C-Ya later! was created out of a desire to have a bioavailable source of Vitamin C readily available and easy to take. Not only does Vitamin C support your immune system, but you need it to form blood vessels and build cartilage, muscle, and collagen in your bones. While C-Ya later! is derived from superfoods (the most concentrated sources of Vitamin C on the planet), unfortunately, most other Vitamin C supplements on the market are derived from Ascorbic Acid. This synthetic compound only gives you a fraction of what you need to support your body. NOTE: This is a 30-day supply and contains 60 capsules. Take 2 capsules per day with water. Ingredients: Amla Extract, Acerola Cherry Extract, Organic Camu Camu, Rose Hips Proudly made in the USA!
